    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those prioritizing function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the driver-side door. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, though the cabin remains comfortable. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some suspension work in the near future. It's a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles of daily use.",
